<div class="prose">
  <p>The five Unit 0 / Unit 3 starter partners cover the most common needs — stress-testing claims, evaluating sources, working through plate-tectonic concepts, reasoning about engineering trade-offs, and rehearsing defenses. <strong>Unit 1 adds two</strong> — the Planet Hunter (exoplanet habitability reasoning) and the Systems Diagrammer (systems-thinking coach). <strong>Unit 2 adds one</strong> — the Field Geologist (landscape-reading partner). <strong>Unit 4 adds two</strong> — the Climate Modeler (IPCC + climate model reasoning) and the Policy Aide (policy-brief voice + panel rehearsal). <strong>Unit 5 adds two</strong> — The Hydrologist (water systems + case-specific hydrology) and The Stakeholder Voice (role-plays specific water-rights stakeholders for perspective-taking work). The Stakeholder Voice is U5's signature partner — in the BoodleBox arm students <em>build</em> their own version of it for their chosen stakeholder. <strong>Unit 6 adds two</strong> — the Urban Planner (urban-form + density reasoning) and the Equity &amp; Resilience Partner (displacement, flood and heat, and the informal-settlement perspective); the two disagree on purpose, and students synthesize them. Each is a separate persona with its own scope.</p>
  <p>All five share the same design principles:</p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Socratic by default.</strong> Each partner asks before telling. You do the thinking; the partner shapes the path.</li>
    <li><strong>Scoped narrowly.</strong> Each has a clear job. Ask the wrong partner the wrong question and you'll be redirected.</li>
    <li><strong>Honest about limits.</strong> Each will say "I might be wrong about this — verify with [primary source]" when uncertain.</li>
    <li><strong>Documentation-ending.</strong> Every substantive conversation ends with a reminder to fill out the <a href="/foundations/ai-documentation-protocol/">AI Documentation Template</a>.</li>
  </ul>
  <p>For the "when to use which partner" decision table, see <a href="/foundations/how-to-use-ai-partners/">How to Use AI Partners</a>.</p>
</div>

